Sentencas: For solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs), biohydrogen is an ideal fuel, which introduces a clean renewable energy source to a highly efficient energy conversion technology with minimum complications.
Titulo: Performance of a biohydrogen solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The performance of a SOFC working with biohydrogen, and the effects of fuel composition, working temperature, load, and air utilization are less well understood.
Titulo: Performance of a biohydrogen solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In this study a comprehensive numerical model was employed to investigate the biohydrogen fueled SOFC in different working conditions.
Titulo: Performance of a biohydrogen solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Direct electrochemical oxidation of H-2 and CO and water gas shift reaction (WGSR) were considered in the model.
Titulo: Performance of a biohydrogen solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: An experimental set up was built to verify the simulation results.
Titulo: Performance of a biohydrogen solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Results from the numerical model were validated against experimental polarization curves and cell temperature measurements.
Titulo: Performance of a biohydrogen solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The results showed how different parameters affect the performance of a biohydrogen SOFC and how different working conditions can be selected to meet certain criteria.
Titulo: Performance of a biohydrogen solid oxide fuel cell
